'''Peter Burroughs''' (born [[January 27]], [[1940s|1947]]) is an actor who played a swinging [[Ewok]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']] and worked on the stunts for the film. Stock footage of his Ewok character in ''Return of the Jedi'' was later used in the video game ''[[Star Wars: Battlefront]]''.

He went on to play a Nelwyn villager in [[Willow (film)|''Willow'']], and worked on the stunts for the film. He has also performed in films such as [[Wikipedia:The Dark Crystal|''The Dark Crystal'']] and [[Wikipedia:Labyrinth (film)|''Labyrinth'']].

Burroughs' daughter, Samantha Davis, is married to actor [[Warwick Davis]].

